Solam, and good day. My name is Setial Stein`Zorbe.

But I must fight on. I like to keep my self happy by dancing; it's quite fun to do. Course you may catch me sun bathing also, but hey, I'm a lizard, so what do ya expect. I love dancing the most though, if you want I'll dance for ya. Just give me a call.
